{"word":"Sufferings of Christ","slug":"sufferings-of-christ","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Sufferings of Christ</b> - <b>(1) General References to</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=69&verse=20'>Psa 69:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=50&verse=6'>Isa 50:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=53&verse=5'>Isa 53:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=38&chapter=13&verse=6'>Zec 13:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=15&verse=34'>Mar 15:34</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=22&verse=44'>Luk 22:44</a><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=2&verse=10'>Heb 2:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=5&verse=8'>Heb 5:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=13&verse=12'>Heb 13:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=60&chapter=1&verse=11'>1Pe 1:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=60&chapter=2&verse=21'>1Pe 2:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=60&chapter=3&verse=18'>1Pe 3:18</a><p/><b>--SEE</b> Sacrifice of Christ, SAVIOUR<p/>Substitution, SAVIOUR<p/>Christ's Death, SAVIOUR<p/><b>(2)</b> Predicted by Himself. See CHRIST'S DIVINITY<p/><b>(3) \"The Man of Sorrows\"</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=53&verse=3'>Isa 53:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=7&verse=34'>Mar 7:34</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=8&verse=12'>Mar 8:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=19&verse=41'>Luk 19:41</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=11&verse=33'>Joh 11:33</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=11&verse=35'>Joh 11:35</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=12&verse=27'>Joh 12:27</a>; <a href